name: Arctic fox
description: The Arctic fox (Vulpes lagopus), also known as the white fox, polar fox,or snow fox, is a small fox that belongs to the family of Canidae

name: Fennec fox
description: The fennec fox (Vulpes zerda) is a small crepuscular fox native to the deserts of North Africa

name: grayfox
description: Gray Fox, Null, y Garganta Profunda fueron los nombres en clave de Frank Jaeger o Frank Hunter, agente de FOX y posteriormente FOXHOUND. Fue el único miembro de FOXHOUND en obtener el nombre en código de Fox

name: Marble fox
description: The Canadian Marble Fox, or Arctic Marble Fox, is a unique and beautiful subspecies of the red fox that is found only in a small area of Canada

name: Red fox
description: The red fox (Vulpes vulpes) is the largest of the true foxes and one of the most widely distributed members of the order Carnivora
